document_data.mainbody: ''Wildwoods''' was a mansion located in the [[King's Forest]] near [[Waymoot]] in [[Cormyr]].
document_data.Inhabitants: The original owner of the mansion was a [[wizard]] named [[Orthaerus Manycloaks]]. Orthaerus was slain during a spell-duel by the traveling wizard [[Endarthar]], who then assumed ownership of the estate.
document_data.Rumors and Legends: After his death, the [[ghost]] of Orthaerus still resided within the mansion, jumping on any opportunity to make Endarthar's life miserable.
